window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The price of normalcy</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>Hoping to cure his curse and return to his fiancée, Jason Wolfe agrees to command a corporate monster-hunting unit. But the team isn’t exactly what he had in mind....</p> <p>A priest, a ninja, a zombie, and a guy who looks like he should be working crew on the carny circuit. To be fair, not all of Jason’s new charges are keen on being trained by a werewolf.&nbsp;</p> <p>But ready or not, the team has just been called to a job. Something is snatching children from a small town in southern Mexico. Worse, all signs point to vampires - and a darker, more malevolent force.&nbsp;</p> <p>As evil grips the vulnerable town, Jason’s ability to lead and his Blue Wolf’s instincts to protect will be challenged like never before, especially as trouble looms back home.&nbsp;</p> <p>Can he rally his misfit crew before the evil claims them? Or will his team’s first mission be its last?&nbsp;</p> <p><b>Blue Wolf series</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>Book 1: <i>Blue Curse </i></p> <p>Book 2: <i>Blue Shadow </i></p> <p>* More to come *&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
